'''Hu Baosen''' is a Chinese businessman and the owner of [[Henan Jianye]] of the [[Chinese Super League]]. He is the founder, owner, and chairman of [[Henan Jianye]], a construction firm. He has been listed by [[Forbes]] as one of China's 400 richest individuals. He is also the owner and chairman of [[Henan Jianye F.C.]]<ref>https://www.forbes.com/lists/2005/74/RC91.html Forbes</ref>

